{"tid":559542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再多4.7萬單程證 本港人口突破740萬","createTime":"2018-02-13T09:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T16:18:47.000Z","uid":42374,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"39f7c083f623da0a8afa42f954a999ae2a528915","tid":559542,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T09:22:25.000Z","msg":"政府統計處公佈，2017年底本港人口的臨時數字為7,409,800人，與之前一年比較，增加了32,700人，增長率為0.4%。2016年底至2017年底的人口自然增長為1萬人，其中出生人數56,600人，死亡人數46,600人。在同期內，淨遷移人數為22,600人，其中有多達47,000單程證持有人的移入，24,300人為其他香港居民的淨移出。<br />\n<br />\n根據統計處的臨時數字，2017底總人口常住居民佔7,182,600人，流動居民佔227,200人。2017年年中人口修訂數字為7,391,700人。常住居民的數字修訂為7,172,800人，流動居民的數字修訂為218,900人。2016年年中至2017年年中的人口增長率亦修訂為0.8%。<br />\n<br />\n支那香港省<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5bd3b53720b9c4428d0cda9159bc765cbce62d","tid":559542,"uid":42374,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T09:22:48.000Z","msg":"有錢嘅快啲走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9102d9b49533a3784dc09ea813c6023baa672755","tid":559542,"uid":42374,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T09:24:05.000Z","msg":"單程證班人仲多過本土出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca72944f857f570411ff29926448361fa336249","tid":559542,"uid":146535,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T09:26:39.000Z","msg":"其中出生人數56,600人，死亡人數46,600人。<br />\n<br />\n個數咁啱1 萬人喎"},{"pid":"621ef5f3be9db43c41c188cc128cf711675acc87","tid":559542,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T09:27:43.000Z","msg":"洗牌洗得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd3ad506f24b3c1fd8134c71b2498a7bdd2e901","tid":559542,"uid":124268,"like